description:
Drama / Music


She gave and gave, until she had nothing left to give 
The story of the tragic life of a self destructive female rock star, modeled after Janis Joplin.
Bette Midler plays "Rose", an artist strikingly similar to Janis Joplin. The film follows Rose&#039;s career during her last tour. Her rock and roll lifestyle of Drugs, Sex, and Rock and Roll and constant touring lead her to an inevitable breakdown


Nominated for 4 Oscars. Another 4 wins & 5 nominations
